extendedInfo.description: Want to know more about the Paleo Diet and what it can do for you? This free app will give you great diet tips, recipes, videos and more. It includes: - Paleo Diet Recipes - Paleo Diet Plans - Paleo Diet Videos - Paleo Diet NewsThis app will specifically help you better understand the Paleo Diet plus offer you information and tips on how you can get more out of it. What more can you ask for? Download it NOW for FREE to get all this great information and more!

I Thought it was just one article but it was the whole app.  Idk if it had to do with the ad at the bottom but I had to uninstall until this is fixed :(
